1. Moja omiljena profesija je *glumac*. (My favorite profession is actor.)
2. Prošle nedelje sam gledao predstavu sa sjajnim *glumcem*. (Last week I watched a play with a brilliant actor.)
3. On je već dugi niz godina uspešan *glumac*. (He has been a successful actor for many years.)
4. *Glumac* je bio oduševljen pozitivnim kritikama za svoju ulogu. (The actor was thrilled with the positive reviews for his role.)
5. Želeo bih da budem *glumac* kada odrastem. (I want to be an actor when I grow up.)
6. Poznati *glumac* će otvoriti novi pozorišni festival. (A famous actor will open a new theater festival.)
7. *Glumcu* su ponudili glavnu ulogu u novom filmu. (The actor was offered the lead role in a new movie.)
8. Ova predstava ima sjajan *glumački* ansambl. (This play has a brilliant cast.)
9. *Glumačka* izvedba je bila neverovatna. (The acting performance was incredible.)
10. Njegova *glumačka* karijera je krenula uzlaznom putanjom. (His acting career is on the rise.)